{"tid":1480962,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【818 - 沙田友入】2:00第一城追擊TVB，2:30出發去維園","createTime":"2019-08-17T13:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:17:50.000Z","uid":267969,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d405bd00488869c50bc1c5f967c17f83c24114","tid":1480962,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:44:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">上次光復沙田</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好多港島人2:00pm 先去紅磡追擊馬明<br />\n2:30pm 即飛去沙田撐光復<br />\n今次到沙田有TVB活動，20-50人叫口號就夠<br />\n沙田友去唔去第一城自己決定喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/WpWEbYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpWEbYj.png&h=d131937b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我都係紅磡去沙田其中一人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>8月18日<br />\n2:00 第一城追擊TVB 鄺潔楹<br />\n2:30出發去維園，地鐵45min內到</strong></span><br />\n雖然維園call time 係2:00pm，但3:15pm去到應該都ok<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kY2Drf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkY2Drf1.jpg&h=b671aa42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>口號，最好粗字print出嚟：</strong></span></span><br />\n無綫新聞 誤導市民<br />\n無綫新聞 包庇差人<br />\n袁志偉下台 黃淑明下台<br />\n抵制廣告商<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記住：</span></strong></span><br />\n見到TVB偽人先叫口號，有小朋友表演就唔好嗌口號，請靜心支持小朋友<br />\n有記者採訪，就要喺記者附近嗌口號，「抵制廣告商」一定要嗌俾記者聽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">TG 狙擊活動行動組:</span></strong></span><br />\n活動最新update 請問TG group admin，利伸本人非admin，只係幫手宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tvbfucker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftvbfucker&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmre6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=73359347\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tvbfucker</a>"},{"pid":"f9e0a374e7fcb3c80326396d30918ac7aaa5eacf","tid":1480962,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:45:10.000Z","msg":"818維園見！所有聽日去嘅人都同我入一入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"64efe0940c922511bdc63e1840ce2c4a82c3e38a","tid":1480962,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:45:30.000Z","msg":"無良心媒體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94397d493966064c9386df87246df3c102dd4e10","tid":1480962,"uid":263973,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"818去維園，主線重要過其他"},{"pid":"783b94506cad71740d6647e70feaf24ff66ce385","tid":1480962,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45632f494b8f07eb2223a0dc342f7550ff72d51","tid":1480962,"uid":267969,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"94397d493966064c9386df87246df3c102dd4e10","tid":1480962,"uid":263973,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"818去維園，主線重要過其他"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:47:31.000Z","msg":"um 冇衝突喎"},{"pid":"a70f03324e4e6897cc68853d5e09f9fd0e77cc14","tid":1480962,"uid":136147,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:52:14.000Z","msg":"沙田友不坊追擊完再出維園 香港人預咗會遲"},{"pid":"097d597e792f586aab51025f71ff1e0074e0b955","tid":1480962,"uid":273593,"like":0,"